    TagMatcher
     
    TypeBits
    Support for bitsets that precisely describe which features to match: - by primitive type - by area flag - by relation membership - whether way has feature nodes, or a feature node belongs to a way We can obtain these bits from the feature flags like this: (flags >> 1) & 0x1F 0 = area flag 1 = relmember flag 2/3 = type 4 = way-node flag This gives us 32 combinations, which neatly fit in an int.
